               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17480907-17-off78-c109" targOrder="Y" targets="t17480907-17-defend144 t17480907-17-off78 t17480907-17-verdict81"></join>
         
               <p>401 + 
               
                  <persName id="t17480907-17-defend144" type="defendantName">
                     John 
                     Kates 
                  <interp inst="t17480907-17-defend144" type="surname" value="Kates"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17480907-17-defend144" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17480907-17-defend144" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17480907-17-off78" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17480907-17-off78" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17480907-17-off78" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing a handkerchief, value 18 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17480907-17-victim146" type="victimName">
                           Benjamin 
                           Johnson 
                        <interp inst="t17480907-17-victim146" type="surname" value="Johnson"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17480907-17-victim146" type="given" value="Benjamin"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17480907-17-victim146" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17480907-17-off78 t17480907-17-victim146"></join>
                     </persName>
                      
                  , privately from his person
            </rs>, the <rs id="t17480907-17-cd79" type="crimeDate">6th of August</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17480907-17-off78 t17480907-17-cd79"></join>.</p>
               <p>Ben. Johnson. On the 6th of August, between twelve and one, I was going under <placeName id="t17480907-17-crimeloc80">Newgate</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17480907-17-crimeloc80" type="placeName" value="Newgate"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17480907-17-crimeloc80" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17480907-17-off78 t17480907-17-crimeloc80"></join>, (and as I had lost three handkerchiefs before, it made me the more cautious ) I thought I felt something bobbing against my pocket, and I saw the prisoner with my handkerchief in his hand, and saw him put it into his bosom; and I took it from him.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17480907-17-verdict81" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17480907-17-verdict81" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17480907-17-verdict81" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty, 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17480907-17-punish82" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17480907-17-punish82" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17480907-17-defend144 t17480907-17-punish82"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
